subsection.def:
business
                    (業務) means business with or without a view to
                profit;

lease
                    (租契) includes a licence, a tenancy agreement
                and an agreement for a lease, licence or tenancy agreement;

non-resident
                    (非居港者) means a non-local individual or
                non-local undertaking;

payment
                    (付款) includes a payment in money or money’s
                worth;

receipt
                    (收入) includes a receipt in money or money’s
                worth;

resident
                    (居港者) means a local individual or local
                undertaking;

survey
                    (調查) means the statistical survey referred to
                in section 2;

paragraph.content:
placing of money in the form of deposits or margin payments by a resident
                    with a non-local undertaking, or by a non-resident with a local
                    undertaking;
